<https://w3id.org/narn/> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An OWL ontology for modeling story plots and narrative structures. It provides a formal vocabulary to represent characters, locations, events, actions, and temporal relations within a narrative."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Formal Model of Story Plots"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/> <https://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2026-03-17"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
