# https://w3id.org/narn/action/causesByAction
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/causesByAction> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/causesByAction> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyChainAxiom> _:genid2 .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid1 .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#nil> .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasResult> .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> _:genid3 .
_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy> .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/causesByAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "If an agent performs an action with a result, the agent indirectly causes that result."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/causesByAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "causes by action"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/causesByAction> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "brings about"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/causesByAction> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Turambar causes the death of Glaurung by performing the slaying."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasCause> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/Action> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An object used to perform the action (e.g. a sword)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has instrument"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "using"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasInstrument> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The Slaying of Glaurung has instrument Gurthang."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasIntention
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasIntention> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasIntention> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasIntention> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasIntention> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/Action> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasIntention> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The goal or purpose behind the action."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasIntention> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has intention"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasIntention> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "aims to"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasIntention> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Túrin's flight from Doriath has the intention of escaping judgement."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasRecipient
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasRecipient> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasRecipient> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasRecipient> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasRecipient> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/TransferAction> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasRecipient> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasRecipient> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The character who receives something in a transfer action."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasRecipient> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has recipient"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasRecipient> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "received by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasRecipient> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Beleg's gift of Anglachel has recipient Túrin."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasResult
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasResult> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/Action> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The event or state that results from the action."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has result"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasResult> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "results in"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasResult> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Brandir's speech results in the truth about Níniel being revealed."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasPatient> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/Action> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The entity that the action is directed towards."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has target"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "directed at"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The Slaying of Glaurung has target Glaurung."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/action/Action> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The agent who intentionally performs the action."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "performed by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "done by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/action/performedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The Slaying of Glaurung was performed by Turambar."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/begets
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/begets> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/begets> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/begets> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Birth> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/begets> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The character brought into existence by a birth event."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/begets> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "begets"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/begets> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "brings forth"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/begets> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The birth of Túrin begets Túrin."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This event causally leads to another event."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "causes"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "leads to"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The death of Saeros causes the exile of Túrin from Doriath."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/creates
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/creates> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/creates> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/creates> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An entity produced or created by the event."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/creates> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "creates"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/creates> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "results in"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/creates> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The reforging of Anglachel creates Gurthang."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasWitness> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The entity that intentionally causes or performs the event."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has agent"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "done by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasAgent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The death of Saeros has agent Túrin."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasCause
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasCause> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasCause> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
