<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasCause> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has cause"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasCause> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "caused by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasCause> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The death of Beleg has cause Anglachel."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasDestination
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasDestination> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasDestination> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt> .
