<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasDestination> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/Place> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasDestination> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasOrigin> .
