<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasDestination> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has destination"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasDestination> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "arrives at"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasDestination> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Túrin's journey has destination Doriath."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasOrigin
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/MovementEvent> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/Place> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The starting place of a movement event."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has origin"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "departs from"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Túrin's journey to Doriath has origin Dor-lómin."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An entity that takes part in the event."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has participant"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "involves"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The Battle of Unnumbered Tears has participant Húrin."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasPatient
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasPatient> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasPatient> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasPatient> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasPatient> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The entity affected by the event."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasPatient> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has patient"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasPatient> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "affects"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasPatient> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Glaurung hypnotises Níniel, with Níniel as the patient."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A smaller event that occurs as part of this one."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has subevent"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "contains event"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The Wars of Beleriand has subevent the Nirnaeth Arnoediad."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasTraveller
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasTraveller> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasTraveller> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasTraveller> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Travel> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasTraveller> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The character who undertakes the travel."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasTraveller> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has traveller"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasTraveller> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "travelled by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasTraveller> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Túrin, Gethron and Grithnir are travellers in the journey to Doriath."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasVictim
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasVictim> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasVictim> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasPatient> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasVictim> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasVictim> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The entity that suffers harm in the event."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasVictim> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has victim"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasVictim> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "harms"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasVictim> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The death of Beleg has victim Beleg."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasWitness
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasWitness> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasWitness> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasParticipant> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasWitness> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasWitness> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An entity that observes the event without acting."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasWitness> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has witness"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasWitness> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "observed by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasWitness> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Mîm's betrayal has witness Andróg."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/isBegottenIn
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isBegottenIn> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isBegottenIn> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/begets> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isBegottenIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isBegottenIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Birth> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isBegottenIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of begets. Links a character to the birth event that brings them into existence."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isBegottenIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is begotten in"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isBegottenIn> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Túrin is begotten in the birth of Túrin."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/isCausedBy
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isCausedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isCausedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/causes> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isCausedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of causes. This event results from another."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isCausedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is caused by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isCausedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "results from"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isCausedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The exile of Túrin is caused by the death of Saeros."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/isSubEventOf
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isSubEventOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isSubEventOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/during> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isSubEventOf> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/hasSubEvent> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isSubEventOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This event is part of a larger event."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isSubEventOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is subevent of"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isSubEventOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "part of event"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/isSubEventOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The Nirnaeth Arnoediad is a subevent of the Wars of Beleriand."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/Place> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The place where the event occurs."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "occurs at"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "takes place at"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/occursAt> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The Captivity of Húrin occurs at Angband."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/to/precedes> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/event/Event> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This event occurs before another event."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "precedes"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "comes before"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/event/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The Nirnaeth Arnoediad precedes Túrin's journey to Doriath."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/location/borders
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/borders> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/borders> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/borders> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/borders> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/borders> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/rcc/DC> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/borders> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Two places share a boundary but neither contains the other."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/borders> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "borders"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/borders> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "adjacent to"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/borders> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Doriath borders Brethil."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/Place> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/Place> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/rcc/DC> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/rcc/EC> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/rcc/PO> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of isAPartOf."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "contains"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "includes"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/contains> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Beleriand contains Doriath."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/Place> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/Place> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A general spatial relation between two places."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has spatial relation"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "spatially related to"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Doriath has a spatial relation to Brethil, as they border each other."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/Place> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/Place> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/rcc/DC> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/rcc/EC> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/narn/rcc/PO> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates that a place constitutes a subarea of another place."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is a part of"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "part of"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isAPartOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Dor-lómin is a part of Hithlum."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/location/isNear
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isNear> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isNear> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/hasSpatialRelation> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isNear> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/isNear> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
