<https://w3id.org/narn/social/killed> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "slew"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/killed> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Túrin engaged in a fatal conflict and killed Saeros."@en .
