_:genid5 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid4 .
_:genid4 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#nil> .
_:genid4 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> <https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheKingOf> .
_:genid4 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
_:genid5 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> <https://w3id.org/narn/social/served> .
