# https://w3id.org/narn/social/loved
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/loved> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/loved> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/social/hasEmotionalRelationWith> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/loved> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates a profound sentiment of affection or love directed at another entity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/loved> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "loved"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/loved> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "had love for"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/loved> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Húrin held a deep affection and loved Morwen."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/social/mutuallyLoved
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/mutuallyLoved> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/mutuallyLoved> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/social/loved> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/mutuallyLoved> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/mutuallyLoved> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Describes a symmetric emotional state where two characters share reciprocal affection."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/mutuallyLoved> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "mutually loved"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/mutuallyLoved> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "reciprocally loved"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/mutuallyLoved> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Turambar and Níniel shared a bond and mutually loved each other."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/social/ruled
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/ruled> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/ruled> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentProperty> <https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheKingOf> .
