<https://w3id.org/narn/social/ruled> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "governed"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/ruled> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Thingol governed and ruled Doriath."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/social/served
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/served> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/served> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/served> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
