# https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/social/livedIn> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/narn/location/Place> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifies a location where a character was forcibly imprisoned or contained."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "was held captive in"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "imprisoned in"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Húrin suffered greatly and was held captive in Angband."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasKilledBy
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasKilledBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasKilledBy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/social/killed> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasKilledBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The inverse relation specifying the perpetrator of a fatal action against the subject."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasKilledBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "was killed by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasKilledBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "slain by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasKilledBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Beleg suffered a tragic fate and was killed by Gorthol."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasServedBy
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasServedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasServedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/social/served> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasServedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The inverse relation designating the superior who receives service."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasServedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "was served by"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasServedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "had as servant"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasServedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Húrin held authority and was served by Sador."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheBestFriendOf
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheBestFriendOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheBestFriendOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/social/hasFriend> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheBestFriendOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheBestFriendOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifies an exceptionally close and prioritized bond of mutual friendship."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheBestFriendOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "was the best friend of"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheBestFriendOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "closest companion of"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheBestFriendOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Beleg proved his loyalty and was the best friend of Túrin."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheChieftainOf
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheChieftainOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
