<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheChieftainOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifies the domain or people over which a character exercised tribal leadership."@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheChieftainOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "was the chieftain of"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheChieftainOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "led as chief"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheChieftainOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Brandir guided his people and was the chieftain of Brethil."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheKingOf
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheKingOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheKingOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheKingOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
