<https://w3id.org/narn/location/Region> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "area"@en .
<https://w3id.org/narn/location/Region> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Beleriand is a region containing Doriath, Hithlum, and Brethil."@en .
